page.title: 08Birds and their Habitat
page.content: We went out birdwatching in our grid from April to July.We saw the following birds and noted their habitats.(Wa= water;Fh=field and hedge;Wo=woodland; Ga=Garden) Mute Swan(WA)Mallard(Wa)Tufted duck(Wa) Kestrel(Fh)Pheasant(Fh)Moorhen(Wa)Wood pigeon(WoFhGa)Collared dove(WoGa)Cuckoo (FhWo)Green woodpecker(Wo)Great Spotted woodpecker(Wo)Skylark(Fh)Swallow (WaFhGa)House martin(GaFhWa)Wren(GaWo) Dunnock(GaFhWo)Robin(GaFhWo)Blackbird (WoFh)Song thrush(WoFhGa)Chiffchaff (WoGa)Spotted flycatcher(WoWaFhGa)Blue tit(WoFhGa)Great tit(WoGaFh) Magpie (Fh Ga)Rook(Fh)Carrion crow(Fh)Starling(Ga FhWo)House sparrow(FhGa)Chaffinch(WoFh Ga)Greenfinch(WoFhGa)Goldfinch(GaFh) Linnet(Wo)Yellowhammer(Fh)Corn bunting Fh)Stock dove(Wo)Whitethroat(Wo).
